1
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:13,779
Didn't you say

2
00:00:13,779 --> 00:00:15,300
you'd do anything for me?

3
00:00:15,579 --> 00:00:17,340
That's because I thought you loved me.

4
00:00:18,539 --> 00:00:19,500
I love you too.

5
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,219
I still love you now.

6
00:00:21,219 --> 00:00:22,460
You don't love me at all.

7
00:00:23,419 --> 00:00:24,860
You've been using me.

8
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:26,860
You've been using me from the start.

9
00:00:38,499 --> 00:00:40,179
It's because you fell in love with my brother, isn't it?

10
00:00:43,419 --> 00:00:44,540
Whatever you think.

11
00:00:45,819 --> 00:00:47,540
Anyway, I won't help you anymore.

12
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:03,740
I got it.

13
00:01:05,019 --> 00:01:05,859
I have an idea.

14
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:28,260
You're here.

15
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:39,900
What's wrong?

16
00:01:47,019 --> 00:01:47,859
I'm sorry.

17
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:52,260
I really didn't know

18
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:54,340
the medicine Mr. Jing gave me was problematic.

19
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:57,260
He told me it was for controlling emotions.

20
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,019
I just wanted you to get better quickly,

21
00:01:59,019 --> 00:02:01,260
so I secretly put it in your wine every day.

22
00:02:01,419 --> 00:02:03,460
But I really didn't know it was problematic.

23
00:02:07,619 --> 00:02:08,980
The doctor told me

24
00:02:10,459 --> 00:02:12,139
that the blindness was caused by the medicine.

25
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,739
But I don't blame you.

26
00:02:18,419 --> 00:02:19,980
Because even if you didn't give me medicine,

27
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:22,859
someone else would have.

28
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,980
But seeing you like this,

29
00:02:27,739 --> 00:02:29,339
I really feel heartbroken

30
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,940
and very guilty.

31
00:02:32,339 --> 00:02:34,060
You know my leg was injured

32
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,700
in a traffic accident, right?

33
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:41,660
But do you really think that was an accident?

34
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,459
I really didn't expect

35
00:02:50,459 --> 00:02:52,060
Mr Jing to be like this.

36
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,459
I used to listen to him,

37
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:56,780
but I won't anymore.

38
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:58,540
I'll only listen to you.

39
00:03:00,019 --> 00:03:01,700
I'm so happy

40
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:04,220
you can tell me this today.

41
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,500
You're the only person

42
00:03:08,579 --> 00:03:09,380
I can trust now.

43
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,299
Xiaoxue,

44
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,419
can you always be with me?

45
00:03:27,299 --> 00:03:28,060
There are some things

46
00:03:28,859 --> 00:03:29,899
that you'll have to handle for me.

47
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:32,060
The art gallery is in your hands now.

48
00:03:32,579 --> 00:03:35,060
I'll do my best.

49
00:03:35,739 --> 00:03:36,500
Ji Xiaoxue,

50
00:03:38,179 --> 00:03:39,339
this is your proposal?

51
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:41,260
The data is inaccurate,

52
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,339
the information is incomplete.

53
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:45,739
Do you not take my words seriously,

54
00:03:45,899 --> 00:03:47,660
or do you not take Mr. Gu's words seriously?

55
00:03:48,459 --> 00:03:50,339
Yeah, it's really not good enough.

56
00:03:50,899 --> 00:03:51,859
Exactly.

57
00:03:51,899 --> 00:03:53,299
The data doesn't even match up.

58
00:03:58,540 --> 00:03:59,619
I'm sorry, Miss Xia.

59
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,179
I'll correct it as soon as possible.

60
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,459
Not as soon as possible,

61
00:04:02,739 --> 00:04:03,660
immediately.

62
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:05,980
I'm sorry.

63
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,260
I...

64
00:04:10,260 --> 00:04:10,899
It's okay.

65
00:04:11,579 --> 00:04:12,380
It's not your fault.

66
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:14,420
Even if you did everything right,

67
00:04:15,219 --> 00:04:16,860
they would still find something to criticize.

68
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:20,459
It's mainly because I didn't do well enough.

69
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,260
Don't worry,

70
00:04:23,539 --> 00:04:24,579
I'll make sure to gather

71
00:04:24,579 --> 00:04:26,060
all the necessary data and documents.

72
00:04:26,219 --> 00:04:27,500
There won't be any mistakes.

73
00:04:29,459 --> 00:04:32,139
It's just that I wasn't clear on some details

74
00:04:33,139 --> 00:04:34,380
of the acquisition contract at the time.

75
00:04:46,339 --> 00:04:47,860
Here, Young Master Yan, have some tea.

76
00:04:54,139 --> 00:04:54,579
Madam.

77
00:04:54,579 --> 00:04:55,380
You're back.

78
00:04:59,579 --> 00:05:00,300
Xiaoxue,

79
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:04,260
I heard you had some issues at work today.

80
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:07,940
Madam, I...

81
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,339
No need to explain to me.

82
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:13,260
I just think Chengyan values you so much,

83
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:15,420
you should try harder.

84
00:05:17,659 --> 00:05:18,779
I think there's no problem.

85
00:05:19,779 --> 00:05:21,060
You think there's no problem?

86
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:23,260
The company must be fine.

87
00:05:23,539 --> 00:05:24,979
You should know better

88
00:05:25,339 --> 00:05:26,620
than me about the company.

89
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:28,899
I know better than you,

90
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,579
so you don't have to worry.

91
00:05:44,219 --> 00:05:45,260
I lost my ring.

92
00:05:46,099 --> 00:05:48,579
Xiaoxue, please help me find it.

93
00:05:58,659 --> 00:05:59,380
Okay.

94
00:06:08,339 --> 00:06:09,139
What's wrong, Xiaoxue?

95
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:14,300
It's nothing. I just bumped it.

96
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:23,459
Madam, your ring.

97
00:06:34,339 --> 00:06:35,539
Be careful.

98
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,899
Don't lose it again.

99
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:48,139
Have you finished?

100
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,139
I've prepared

101
00:06:51,139 --> 00:06:52,099
all the documents you asked.

102
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:55,579
And these.

103
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,139
What's wrong?

104
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:03,420
Nothing.

105
00:07:06,899 --> 00:07:08,219
Did Qi Zhu do this today?

106
00:07:08,779 --> 00:07:10,060
Why don't you just say it?

107
00:07:10,539 --> 00:07:12,219
I can't confront her now.

108
00:07:12,659 --> 00:07:14,380
If she takes advantage of this,

109
00:07:14,659 --> 00:07:15,740
it will be bad for you.

110
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:18,180
The most important thing for us now

111
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,820
is to get the Su's Art Gallery

112
00:07:19,820 --> 00:07:20,579
ready.

113
00:07:31,459 --> 00:07:32,260
Ji Xiaoxue,

114
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:34,620
you can go.

115
00:07:35,219 --> 00:07:36,420
I haven't finished sorting out yet.

116
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:38,060
You don't have to stay with me.

117
00:07:38,139 --> 00:07:39,420
I'll help you to rest first.

118
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:42,219
I mean you should leave the Gu family.

119
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,700
I know you're worried about me.

120
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,339
Don't worry, I'm fine.

121
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:53,820
I knew it was a trap from the beginning.

122
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,700
You and Gu Chengjing teamed up to trick me,

123
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:57,779
right?

124
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:01,820
Don't say that.

125
00:08:02,099 --> 00:08:03,659
I know you're trying to upset me,

126
00:08:03,659 --> 00:08:04,420
so you're saying that.

127
00:08:04,420 --> 00:08:06,219
Stop pretending to be affectionate.

128
00:08:06,339 --> 00:08:07,700
I knew you were

129
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:09,380
deliberately making me fall in love with you.

130
00:08:10,099 --> 00:08:11,620
So you can tolerate

131
00:08:11,979 --> 00:08:13,060
whatever I do to you.

132
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:14,860
You know, Gu Chengjing

133
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:16,219
hired many nurses for me,

134
00:08:16,339 --> 00:08:17,380
but I drove them away.

135
00:08:18,019 --> 00:08:19,659
So you can tolerate

136
00:08:19,659 --> 00:08:21,060
whatever I do to you.

137
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,260
You succeeded.

138
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,740
You can feed me medicine in various forms.

139
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,099
So I'm blind now,

140
00:08:27,459 --> 00:08:29,300
but the doctor will find the cause sooner or later.

141
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:32,339
You just staged a sad play in advance,

142
00:08:32,579 --> 00:08:34,820
shirked your responsibility,

143
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:36,820
and then won my sympathy.

144
00:08:37,379 --> 00:08:38,020
Right?

145
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:40,259
I really like you.

146
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:41,979
Like me?

147
00:08:42,579 --> 00:08:43,820
Don't you just want to marry into the Gu family,

148
00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:44,900
and marry into a rich family?

149
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,660
I did want to marry you before,

150
00:08:48,859 --> 00:08:50,180
but I've thought it through.

151
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:51,540
How could I possibly marry someone

152
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:53,140
who secretly drugged me?

153
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,700
You treated me like this when I was well before.

154
00:08:56,940 --> 00:08:58,020
I'm blind now.

155
00:08:58,219 --> 00:08:59,499
Isn't it more convenient for you?
